      "protagonist": {
        "name": "Casey Miller",
        "role": "Last Sane Person",
        "description": "Casey Miller is the middle child with a dry sense of humor and permanent eye twitches from keeping the Miller household together. Armed with wit, a half-buttoned flannel, and weary optimism, Casey is determined to survive dinner without a meltdown. They have a knack for solving problems, even if everything around them descends into chaotic comedy.",
